description:
As a user
  I want to be able to register and login
  So that I can access the JobHunt AI application

steps.name: I am on the login page
I fill in the registration form with valid data
I should be successfully registered and logged in

result.error_message: Timed out retrying after 10000ms: Expected to find content: 'Welcome,' but never did.

steps.name: I am on the login page
I fill in the registration form with invalid data
I should see registration error messages
I am on the login page
I fill in the login form with valid credentials
I should be successfully logged in

result.error_message: Timed out retrying after 10000ms: Expected to find content: 'Welcome back,' but never did.

steps.name: I am on the login page
I fill in the login form with invalid credentials
I should see login error messages

result.error_message: Timed out retrying after 10000ms: Expected to find content: 'Invalid email or password' but never did.

steps.name: I am on the login page
I fill in the login form with demo account credentials
I should be successfully logged in

result.error_message: Timed out retrying after 10000ms: Expected to find content: 'Welcome back,' but never did.

steps.name: I should see the dashboard with existing data
I am logged in to the application
I click the logout button in the sidebar
I should see the login page
I try to access a protected route directly
I should be redirected to the login page
I am logged in to the application

name: User Authentication
